snippet.title: Let's Play Rara Racer
snippet.description:
(You can watch parts 5-8 of this review uncut and in high definition on my channel.)


EDIT: I am having trouble uploading my Let's Play videos in HD. I've decided to reupload my Let's Play of Rara Racer in standard definition for now. I may upload the other reviews once I figure out how HD works.

Also for some reason, when I reuploaded this video, YouTube added another minute to it, not that it really matters or anything but its still kinda strange. Yeah, I tend to notice little minute details like that, go figure.
